{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781719619997,"sessionID":"ses_1293d8f5cffeM0kbBvfYyfngHB","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_02_FYrNaMWtmirV3Fjixthj6055","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Strategy: maintenance-grace daemon survives re-election\n\n## topic\nReview of spec-folder `019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection` — the maintenance-active marker that lets launchers adopt a busy-but-healthy daemon during re-election instead of reaping it mid-scan.\n\n## review-dimensions\n\n- [ ] D1 Correctness (Priority 1)\n- [ ] D2 Security (Priority 2)\n- [ ] D3 Traceability / Spec-Alignment (Priority 3)\n- [ ] D4 Maintainability (Priority 4)\n\n## completed-dimensions\n\n(None yet)\n\n## running-findings\n\nP0: 0 | P1: 0 | P2: 0\n\n## what-worked\n\n(None yet)\n\n## what-failed\n\n(None yet)\n\n## exhausted-approaches\n\n(None yet)\n\n## ruled-out-directions\n\n(None yet)\n\n## next-focus\n\nD1 Correctness — verify the daemon marker writer, launcher supervision predicate, and both launcher guard sites implement the spec faithfully and handle edge cases correctly. Focus files: `lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts`, `handlers/memory-index.ts` (lines 1496-1542), `tests/launcher-maintenance-guard.vitest.ts`, `tests/maintenance-marker.vitest.ts`.\n\n## known-context\n\nThis is a fan-out lineage (p019-deepseek-2) in the review fan-out for spec 019. The implementation shipped the maintenance-active marker, pure supervision predicate, and both launcher guard sites. The spec is Level 1 with 4 requirements (REQ-001 through REQ-004). The implementation summary confirms: build passes, syntax checks pass, unit tests pass, isolated harness passes, and a full live reindex completed in 330s on the live daemon.\n\nresource-map.md not present. Skipping coverage gate.\n\n## cross-reference-status\n\n| Protocol | Level | Status | Gate | Notes |\n|----------|-------|--------|------|-------|\n| spec_code | core | pending | hard | Will verify normative claims in spec.md against implementation |\n| checklist_evidence | core | pending | hard | No checklist.md present (Level 1) — protocol is N/A |\n| feature_catalog_code | overlay | pending | advisory | N/A for this target |\n| playbook_capability | overlay | pending | advisory | N/A for this target |\n\n## files-under-review\n\n| File | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| `lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts` | pending | Daemon marker writer (REQ-001) |\n| `handlers/memory-index.ts` (L1496-1542) | pending | Marker integration in background scan |\n| `tests/launcher-maintenance-guard.vitest.ts` | pending | Unit test for supervision predicate |\n| `tests/maintenance-marker.vitest.ts` | pending | Unit test for marker writer |\n| `spec.md` | pending | Normative spec claims |\n| `implementation-summary.md` | pending | Implementation evidence |\n\n## review-boundaries\n\n- Max iterations: 1\n- Convergence threshold: 0.10\n- Severity threshold: P2\n- Execution mode: auto\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-deepseek-2/deep-review-strategy.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-deepseek-2/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-deepseek-2/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1781719619994,"end":1781719619996}},"id":"prt_ed6c3bdbd001RlUm7EnRcWYDU8","sessionID":"ses_1293d8f5cffeM0kbBvfYyfngHB","messageID":"msg_ed6c3a2380019Byil5CjLuPRh7"}}
